		{ ref: `Hebrews 12:1-2`, slug: `hebrews`, ch: 12, text: `Lay aside every weight, and run with endurance the race set before you, fixing your eyes on Jesus, who for the joy set before Him endured the cross.`, note: `The race is long — drop what slows you and keep your eyes on the One who already finished for you.` },
