		{ ref: `Isaiah 40:31`, slug: `isaiah`, ch: 40, text: `Those who hope in your Father will renew their strength; they will soar on wings like eagles, run and not grow weary, walk and not faint.`, note: `When your tank is empty, your Father is the source of strength that doesn't run dry.` },
		{ ref: `2 Timothy 4:7`, slug: `2-timothy`, ch: 4, text: `I have fought the good fight, I have finished the race, I have kept the faith.`, note: `Faithfulness, not the final score, is the finish line that matters most to your Father.` },
