		{ heading: `You meet God as a Father, not a rulebook`, bodyHtml: `Most Bibles can read like a list of expectations — one more coach grading your effort. The Father's Heart Bible™ reveals God as a <em>Father</em> wherever Scripture does — from <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/genesis/1" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Genesis 1</a> on. So instead of one more voice telling you to perform, you meet the One who already delights in you.` },
		{ heading: `It's free, on your phone, with audio`, bodyHtml: `No account, no purchase, no app. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Read it free online</a> with audio on every chapter — listen on the bus to an away game, in the locker room before warmups, or when the loss keeps you up at night. The Father's voice fits right into your training day.` },
