		{ question: `Is there a free Bible with audio for athletes?`, answer: `Yes. The Father's Heart Bible™ is free to read and listen to online — no account, no purchase, no app. Open fathersheartbible.com/read on your phone and read or hear any book — perfect for the bus to an away game, the locker room, or a sleepless night after a tough loss.` },
		{ question: `What makes the Father's Heart Bible™ different for athletes?`, answer: `It's the first English translation to reveal God as Father wherever Scripture reveals Him as Father — so instead of reading one more voice telling you to perform, you meet the One who already delights in you. For an athlete under constant pressure to win, that reframes everything: you come to the Bible as a loved child first, not a competitor being graded. Read it free at fathersheartbible.com/read.` },
	]}
